title: Spanish civil war imminent? Agressive Spanish King on Catalonia independence
description:
Spain's King Felipe VI said the Catalan independence vote "undermined harmony" and the rule of law.
In a TV address to the nation he criticised the organisers for risking the prosperity and peace of the entire country.
